syntax.model:
ind60 =~ JaspColumn_3_Encoded + JaspColumn_6_Encoded + JaspColumn_9_Encoded
  dem60 =~ JaspColumn_12_Encoded + JaspColumn_15_Encoded + JaspColumn_18_Encoded + JaspColumn_21_Encoded
  dem65 =~ JaspColumn_24_Encoded + JaspColumn_27_Encoded + JaspColumn_30_Encoded + JaspColumn_33_Encoded

  dem60 ~ ind60
  dem65 ~ ind60 + dem60

  JaspColumn_12_Encoded ~~ JaspColumn_24_Encoded
  JaspColumn_15_Encoded ~~ JaspColumn_21_Encoded + JaspColumn_27_Encoded
  JaspColumn_18_Encoded ~~ JaspColumn_30_Encoded
  JaspColumn_21_Encoded ~~ JaspColumn_33_Encoded
  JaspColumn_27_Encoded ~~ JaspColumn_33_Encoded
syntax.modelOriginal:
# measurement model
  ind60 =~ x1 + x2 + x3
  dem60 =~ y1 + y2 + y3 + y4
  dem65 =~ y5 + y6 + y7 + y8
# regressions
  dem60 ~ ind60
  dem65 ~ ind60 + dem60
# residual correlations
  y1 ~~ y5
  y2 ~~ y4 + y6
  y3 ~~ y7
  y4 ~~ y8
  y6 ~~ y8

footnotes.text: Estimator is ML. Model test is standard.
